name: self reflection-digital print
description:
picture was taken with film and a hasselblad.
it was digitally printed on fuji crystal archival pearl with chromira.
the paper contains natural mica and titanium dioxide to create a pearl/metallic appearance within the print.
it is real photo paper, and the print has the tactile look and feel of a traditional photograph.
very beautiful!

the image measures 5x5
it is printed on 6x6 paper so you have a nice border suitable for framing.

your photograph will come shipped in a sturdy photo mailer,
with an archival backing board and archival crystal sleeve.
it will be signed on the back.
